rdsample <- readRDS(file="dti_rdsample.rds")
excemptstates <- c("Colorado","Maryland","Vermont","New York","Connecticut")
ggplot()+geom_density(data=rdsample[dti_calc >=40 & dti_calc<=60 & !state %in% excemptstates],aes(x=dti_calc,fill=decision_status,color=decision_status),alpha=0.75)+theme_minimal()+labs(x="Debt-to-income (%)",y="Density")+theme(strip.text.x = element_text(face="bold"))+ scale_fill_manual( values = c("dodgerblue","skyblue"))+ scale_color_manual( values = c("dodgerblue","skyblue"))+theme(legend.position = "bottom",legend.title = element_blank())

dtisummary <- rdsample[dti_calc >=20 & dti_calc<70 & !state %in% excemptstates,.(funded=mean(funded)*100),by=dtibin]
dtisummary[,dtigt50:=ifelse(dtibin>=50,1,0)]


r <- lm(funded~dtibin*dtigt50,data=dtisummary)

dtisummary[,predfunded:=predict(r,dtisummary)]

ggplot()+geom_point(data=dtisummary,aes(x=dtibin,y=funded))+
  geom_line(data=dtisummary[dtigt50==0],aes(x=dtibin,y=predfunded),color="skyblue",size=1)+
  geom_line(data=dtisummary[dtigt50==1],aes(x=dtibin,y=predfunded),color="dodgerblue",size=1)+
  theme_minimal()+labs(x="Debt-to-income",y="Percent funded (%)")

rdsample <- rdsample[!is.na(creditcard_utilization) & !is.na(total_balance_0) & cc_del90==0  & !is.na(vantage_score_0) & creditcard_utilization>0 & total_balance_0>0 & credit_history>0]
mindti = 40
maxdti= 60

r <- list()
r[[1]] <- felm(funded~dtigt50*dti_calc+poly(vantage_score_0,2)+log(1+annual_income)+borrower_age+I(borrower_age^2)+log(1+number_of_accounts)+log(1+inquiries_0)+poly(total_balance_0,2)+poly(credit_history,2)+log(1+num_accounts_opened_in_past_12_months)+log(1+revolving_pct*100)+log(1+mortgage_pct*100)+poly(creditcard_utilization,2)+log(1+g051s_percentage_of_trades_ever_delinquent*100)|appyear_zip,data=rdsample[dti_calc>=mindti & dti_calc<=maxdti ])

r[[2]] <- felm(fico_score_0~dtigt50*dti_calc+log(1+annual_income)+borrower_age+I(borrower_age^2)+log(1+number_of_accounts)+log(1+inquiries_0)+poly(total_balance_0,2)+poly(credit_history,2)+log(1+num_accounts_opened_in_past_12_months)+log(1+revolving_pct*100)+log(1+mortgage_pct*100)+poly(creditcard_utilization,2)+log(1+g051s_percentage_of_trades_ever_delinquent*100)|appyear_zip|0|zip_code,data=rdsample[dti_calc>=mindti & dti_calc<=maxdti  ])

r[[3]] <- felm(log(1+annual_income)~dtigt50*dti_calc+poly(vantage_score_0,2)+borrower_age+I(borrower_age^2)+log(1+number_of_accounts)+log(1+inquiries_0)++poly(total_balance_0,2)+poly(credit_history,2)+log(1+num_accounts_opened_in_past_12_months)+log(1+revolving_pct*100)+log(1+mortgage_pct*100)+poly(creditcard_utilization,2)+log(1+g051s_percentage_of_trades_ever_delinquent*100)|appyear_zip,data=rdsample[dti_calc>=mindti & dti_calc<=maxdti ])

r[[4]] <- felm(log(1+inquiries_0)~dtigt50*dti_calc+poly(vantage_score_0,2)+log(1+annual_income)+borrower_age+I(borrower_age^2)+log(1+number_of_accounts)+poly(total_balance_0,2)+poly(credit_history,2)+log(1+num_accounts_opened_in_past_12_months)+log(1+revolving_pct*100)+log(1+mortgage_pct*100)+poly(creditcard_utilization,2)+log(1+g051s_percentage_of_trades_ever_delinquent*100)|appyear_zip,data=rdsample[dti_calc>=mindti & dti_calc<=maxdti  ])

r[[5]] <- felm(log(1+total_balance_0)~dtigt50*dti_calc+poly(vantage_score_0,2)+log(1+annual_income)+borrower_age+I(borrower_age^2)+log(1+number_of_accounts)++log(1+inquiries_0)+poly(credit_history,2)+log(1+num_accounts_opened_in_past_12_months)+log(1+revolving_pct*100)+log(1+mortgage_pct*100)+poly(creditcard_utilization,2)+log(1+g051s_percentage_of_trades_ever_delinquent*100)|appyear_zip,data=rdsample[dti_calc>=mindti & dti_calc<=maxdti  ])

r[[6]] <- felm(credit_history~dtigt50*dti_calc+poly(vantage_score_0,2)+log(1+annual_income)+borrower_age+I(borrower_age^2)+log(1+number_of_accounts)++log(1+inquiries_0)+poly(total_balance_0,2)+log(1+num_accounts_opened_in_past_12_months)+log(1+revolving_pct*100)+log(1+mortgage_pct*100)+poly(creditcard_utilization,2)+log(1+g051s_percentage_of_trades_ever_delinquent*100)|year|0|appyear_zip,data=rdsample[dti_calc>=mindti & dti_calc<=maxdti  ])

r[[7]] <- felm(number_of_accounts_0~dtigt50*dti_calc+poly(vantage_score_0,2)+log(1+annual_income)+borrower_age+I(borrower_age^2)+log(1+number_of_accounts)++log(1+inquiries_0)+poly(total_balance_0,2)+log(1+num_accounts_opened_in_past_12_months)+log(1+revolving_pct*100)+log(1+mortgage_pct*100)+poly(creditcard_utilization,2)+log(1+g051s_percentage_of_trades_ever_delinquent*100)|year|0|appyear_zip,data=rdsample[dti_calc>=mindti & dti_calc<=maxdti  ])
